      • Monster

        public Monster(java.lang.String name,
               int monsterType,
               int health,
               int monstersWalkDistanceX,
               int monstersWalkDistanceY,
               int resourceReward,
               int monsterSize,
               int whichSide,
               int respawnTime)
        Constructor for a monster object, which will set all necessary components. Constructor will also set necessary default monster cords.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of monster
        monsterType - type of monster 0-Goblin 1-Grue 2-Golem 3-Bat 4-Spider
        health - Health of monster
        monstersWalkDistanceX - Monster walk speed X
        monstersWalkDistanceY - Monster walk speed Y
        resourceReward - Reward for a monster
        monsterSize - Monster additional size
        whichSide - Number of lane he will be walking on.
        respawnTime - Time that must pass, to respawn this monster.
